  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to evaluate the effect of a perioperative nutrition strategy
      using oral nutritional supplements (ONS) on postoperative complications and improvement in
      body weight in malnourished patients who underwent gastrectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
